<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport"
content="width=device-width,
initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Assignment-2</title>
<style>
*{
box-sizing: border-box;
margin:0;
padding:0;
}
:root {
--primary-color: blue;
--content-bg:#90EE90;
--border-color: black;
--spacing-unit: 10px;
}
body {
font-family: Aerial, sars-srrif;
padding: 20px;
}
h1 {
margin-bottom: 30px;
color: #333;
}
.box{
background-color: var(--primary-color);
padding: var(--spacing-unit);
border: 3px solid var(--border-color);
margin: 40px 40px 40px 40px;
width: 100px;
border-radius: 4px;
}
.content{
background-color: var(--content-bg);
padding: 15px;
line-height: 1.5;
border-radius: 4px;
color: #333;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
.box {
margin: 20px;
width: auto;
}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Assignment 2</h1>
<div class="box">
<div class="content">Coding is a very important and excitement topic.It's to be learned by everyone.
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
